# entries are BTENTRY (8-byte BREF.bid + 8-byte BREF.ib + key... wait, BTENTRY
# layout per sec 2.2.2.7.7.2 is: btkey (8 B) + BREF (16 B) = 24 bytes. cbEnt=0x18=24.
